    <element xsi:type="archimate:BusinessProcess" name="Digital Transformation Process" id="id-2c009afe05194b15bbef1a40757e3a87">
      <documentation>Reconfiguring Offerings &amp; Value Propositions. Represents an internal operational change to business offerings.</documentation>
